videos.headline: Ohio QB Nathan Rourke calls his own number for TD
videos.description: Bobcats QB Nathan Rourke powers his way in for a touchdown to put Ohio up 21-0.

videos.headline: Cincinnati's Warren II takes it to the house for 24-yd TD
videos.description: Bearcats RB Michael Warren II puts the pedal to the metal for a 24-yard touchdown and gets Cincinnati on the board.

videos.headline: Cincinnati QB Ridder goes deep for 77-yd TD
videos.description: Bearcats QB Desmond Ridder lets one fly to WR Rashad Medaris for a 77-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Cincinnati QB Ridder stiff arms defender in 7-yd run for a TD
videos.description: Bearcats QB Desmond Ridder stiff arms a defender after calling his own number and running for a 7-yard score.
